name: Period 3 Trebuchets
tagline: A website dedicated to the development of trebuchets in iDEA.
body:
### Home
This website features the trebuchet development in Ms. Bostrom's Period 3 Physics class.

### About
We're the class of 2020, and this is the first year iDEA has existed. We're working hard to make it ours.

### Development
All the groups made slings that successfully held the projectile at least once.

    Authors and Contributors
    Website: Aiden, Sam, Will
    Video: Alexis, Jack
